Class PoolTaskServiceImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.dspace.xmlworkflow.storedcomponents.PoolTaskServiceImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DSpaceCRUDService<PoolTask>, PoolTaskService
    public class PoolTaskServiceImpl
extends Object
implements PoolTaskService
    Service implementation for the PoolTask object. This class is responsible for all business logic calls for the PoolTask object and is autowired by spring. This class should never be accessed directly.
    Author:
    kevinvandevelde at atmire.com
